OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FTransparent mouse could    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fimprove cancer drug tests  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A new scanning method involving a      
OL,6, see-through mouse could improve how    
OL,7, cancer drugs are tested, by picking up 
OL,8, tumours previously too small to detect.
OL,10,FProf Ali Erturk of the Helmholtz Munich
OL,11,Fresearch centre worked out how to make 
OL,12,Fa dead mouse transparent in 2018.      
OL,14,FHis team have now used chemicals to    
OL,15,Fhighlight specific tissues so that they
OL,16,Fcan be scanned in unprecedented detail.
OL,18,FDrugs are often tested first on mice.  
OL,19,FScientists say the new scanning method 
OL,20,Fcould revolutionise medical research.  
